summary:
I am master degree holder in Food biotechnology from Wageningen University-Netherlands, I am working as part time assistant Lecturer at INES-University-Northern province of Rwanda.(http://ines.ac.rw/)
I am interested in pursuing my higher studies in Food biotechnology related research(PhD).
